    arm64: dts: qcom: add Canoe IMEM

    Describe the 4 KiB IMEM window at 0x14680000 and expose the PIL
    relocation table at offset 0x94c for future remoteproc consumers.

    Limit this milestone to the generic mainline IMEM parent and supported
    PIL relocation child; downstream-only debug and restart-reason children
    remain out of scope.

